    <h4>Acceptance of User Agreement:</h4>
    <p>This user agreement is valid, binding and enforceable against all persons who access this website or any part thereof. Please read this user agreement carefully as by using this website you will be taken to have agreed to be bound by it. If you do not agree to be bound by the provisions of this user agreement, you must leave the TravelGround.com website immediately as further use will automatically bind you to this user agreement, notwithstanding any disagreements by you to the terms of this policy.</p>

    <h4>Allowed use of information on this website:</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>
        You may only access and browse this website for legitimate personal and non-commercial purposes and may not use this website for:        <ul>
          <li>i) harmful purposes; or</li>
