    <h4>Correctness of your information:</h4>
    <p>You hereby undertake to ensure that all of the information that you supply to TravelGround.com is correct and continuously updated, including, but not limited to, your name and residential address. TravelGround.com shall not be liable for any damage, loss or liability of whatsoever nature arising from any misrepresentation by you. In the event that you fail to keep your information current and updated, we reserve the right to suspend or remove your TravelGround.com account.</p>

