    <p>TravelGround.com reserves the right to vary this policy at any time, without prior notice or justification. Any such changes will be posted on this page. You are encouraged to review this privacy policy at the inception of each session, as you will be deemed to have accepted any such changes (which shall come into effect once posted on this website) if you continue to use this website after they have been posted.</p>

